author: Josh Margolin, James Gordon Meek
title: Intelligence report warned of coronavirus crisis as early as November: Sources
description: "Analysts concluded it could be a cataclysmic event," a source says.
content: As far back as late November, U.S. intelligence officials were warning that a contagion was sweeping through Chinas Wuhan region, changing the patterns of life and business and posing a threat to the population, according to four sources briefed on the secret… [+7313 chars]
